### Get Cardiologists
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/hospital/Doctors?$filter=specialization eq 'Cardiologist'

###

### Get appointments for date
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/hospital/Appointments?$filter=appointmentDate eq 2026-06-01

###

### Create Patient
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/hospital/Patients
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName":"Test",
  "lastName":"Patient",
  "dateOfBirth":"1999-01-01",
  "gender":"Male",
  "bloodGroup":"O_POS",
  "phone":"9999999999",
  "email":"test@gmail.com",
  "address":"Delhi",
  "emergencyContact":"8888888888",
  "registrationDate":"2026-06-01"
}

###

### Create Appointment
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/hospital/Appointments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patient_ID":"pat1",
  "doctor_ID":"doc1",
  "appointmentDate":"2026-06-10",
  "appointmentTime":"10:30:00",
  "reason":"General Checkup",
  "fee":1000
}

###

### Get Patients by Blood Group
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/hospital/Patients?$filter=bloodGroup eq 'O_POS'

###

### Update Appointment Status
PATCH http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/hospital/Appointments('app1')
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "Completed"
}